address.streetAddress: 536 Via De La Valle UNIT C

location.fullValue: 536 Via De La Valle UNIT C

data.description: Enter the very large courtyard from your 2 car garage to this single level 2 bedroom, 2 bath condo. Very private patio's. Light and bright with raised ceilings.  Master bedroom begins walking through etched French doors. All closets through-out are cedar lined and have built in organized shelfs.  Doors are covered with mirrors. The bright kitchen nook overlooks a very private courtyard.   Two large dual-pane skylights open to the night sky.  Great area for walking around the community and entertaining.  Easy access to shops across the street, La Valle Coastal golf club and freeways. Laundry in garage.
